sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice
    participant Server
    participant Bob

    Alice->>Server: hello(roomId)
    Server-->>Alice: initialDocument (if room exists)

    Alice->>Server: sync(events, frontiers)
    Server-->>Alice: sync(missingEvents, frontiers)

    Bob->>Server: hello(roomId)
    Server-->>Bob: initialDocument

    Bob->>Server: sync(events, frontiers)
    Server-->>Bob: sync(missingEvents, frontiers)

    Note over Alice,Bob: Both connected, editing concurrently

    Alice->>Server: sync([alice:4, alice:5], frontiers)
    Server-->>Bob: sync([alice:4, alice:5], frontiers)

    Bob->>Server: sync([bob:0, bob:1], frontiers)
    Server-->>Alice: sync([bob:0, bob:1], frontiers)

    Note over Alice,Bob: Both peers converge to same state
